Package es.backend.meetup.dto

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CitiesResultDTO
    CitiesResultDTO is the object returned when querying for cities with most events on a date
    CityDTO
    CityDTO is the object containing the city data to return in requests
    CityResultDTO
    CityDTO is the object containing the city result containing the city data and the number of events to return in requests
    ErrorDTO
    ErrorDTO is the object returned in case an error occurs during a request
    EventDTO
    EventDTO is the object containing the event data retrieved from the Meetup stream
    GroupDTO
    GroupDTO is the object containing the group data obtained from the Meetup stream and returned in requests.
    GroupResultDTO
    GroupResultDTO is the object containing the group data and the distance in km to return in requests
    GroupsNearResultDTO
    GroupsNearResultDTO is the object returned when querying for groups closer to a given locations
    ListenerStatusDTO
    ListenerStatusDTO is the object returned when requesting for an action (start/stop) on the stream listener.
    MemberDTO
    MemberDTO is the object containing the member data obtained from the Meetup stream.
    ResultDTO<T>
    ResultDTO is the generic object to return the Meetup data request results.
    RsvpDTO
    RsvpDTO is the main object containing the RSVP data retrieved from the Meetup stream
    VenueDTO
    VenueDTO is the object containing the venue data obtained from the Meetup stream.
